:DT.case
:I2 refid='lacase'.lacase
:DD.This attribute accepts the keyword values :hp1.mixed:ehp1.,
    :HP1.upper:eHP1. and :hp1.lower:ehp1..
    When a heading is processed, the text is converted to upper
    or lower case when the values UPPER or LOWER are used.
    The text is left unchanged when the value MIXED is used.
